  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to describe differences in meal-stimulated gut hormone response,
      appetite and intestinal transit time between good and poor responders 1-2 years after Gastric
      Bypass surgery for obesity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
